						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Super Mario Bros 3: after the 2nd level, enter the bonus round (the one with scrolling mushroom/flower/star). Press the button to make the top bar stop, and now the bottom line of this bar will scroll wrongly. It will also happen at the 2nd bar. </div>
<br />
<br />This is confirmed to happen on the real hardware - modifications to the fine X-scroll value (bottom 3 bits of first write to $2005) take effect immediately while coarse scroll (upper 5 bits of first write to $2005) are only applied at the beginning of each scanline.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
